text: Edmund Jagiełło (14 November 1946 – 11 November 2020) was a Polish politician and physician. He was a member of the Sejm from 1989 to 1991. He later was a Senator from 1991 to 1993. He was a member of the Polish United Workers' Party. Jagiełło died on 11 November 2020 in Warsaw, aged 73. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Polish politicians Category:Polish physicians
